Package worldofzuul

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    This class handles user-given commands.
    CommandWords
    Class for presenting and small manipulation of commands defined in the enum object CommandWord in a key-value pair map object.
    Game
    Game class - most of the game is handled from here.
    Parser
    This class receives user input and manipulates it to a single or double word command defined in CommandsWords class.
    Room
    Class to instantiate rooms from.
    StartGame
    This class instantiates the game and is the starting point of the project.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CommandWord
    Enum type for commands assigned as constants.
